<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٣ص١٥٢:</span> وَقَالَتْ عَائِشَةُ: <span class="c2">«هُوَ عَبْدٌ مَا بَقِيَ عَلَيْهِ شَيْءٌ»</span> ,<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ زَيْدُ بْنُ ثَابِتٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَا بَقِيَ عَلَيْهِ دِرْهَمٌ»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>